response.overview: Trainees in the FBI's psychological profiling program must put their training into practice when they discover a killer in their midst.  Based very loosely on Agatha Christie's And Then There Were None.
response.tagline: For seven elite profilers, finding a serial killer is a process of elimination. Their own.
response.title: Mindhunters

titles.title: Mindhunters - Nella mente del serial killer

release_dates.note: Brussels International Festival of Fantasy Films
